  <U n="notification">
    <T p="InGame\UI\Icons\Debug\missing_image.png" n="icon">2f7d0004:00000000:30f0846c783606f9</T>
    <T n="text">0xE48A7866<!--String: "Click to learn more about Fences and Gates."--></T>
    <T n="title">0x68C66726<!--String: "Fences and Gates"--></T>
    <L n="ui_responses">
      <U>
        <T n="text">0xA13F0B8C<!--String: "Learn More   NOT USED"--></T>
        <E n="ui_request">SHOW_LESSONS</E>
      </U>
    </L>
  </U>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\FencesGates_01.png">2f7d0004:00000000:73a831f8108f12a1</T>
      <T n="text">0xF0F36FA3<!--String: "Fences and Gates can be found in the Build catalog by clicking on their sorts in the House Portrait.\n\nThere are two ways to build fences:  by placing them on an existing wall / fence or by drawing them with the Fence Tool."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\FencesGates_02.png">2f7d0004:00000000:73a831f8108f12a2</T>
      <T n="text">0x2FF88995<!--String: "Select the Replace Fences tool from the Fences catalog. Then select a fence style. Click on an existing wall / fence to replace all wall segments along one side of a Room with the chosen fence.\n\nHold [shift] to replace the entire Room, or [alt] to just replace a single wall segment."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\FencesGates_03.png">2f7d0004:00000000:73a831f8108f12a3</T>
      <T n="text">0xB7983487<!--String: "Select the Place Fences by Drawing or Place Fence Enclosure to begin drawing a fence. When drawing a fence, you can make two types: terrain fence or wall railing.\n\nIf you start drawing on the ground, you'll get a yard fence."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\FencesGates_04.png">2f7d0004:00000000:73a831f8108f12a4</T>
      <T n="image_console" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\console\Lessons\FencesGates_04_controller.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c154030180e6df2f</T>
      <T n="text">0xE78D36C5<!--String: "Yard fences are similar to walls, but do not create floors when enclosed, and can't be widened though their length can be adjusted. And their only context menu option is remove them.\n\nNote: You can also delete them with the Sledgehammer Tool."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\FencesGates_05.png">2f7d0004:00000000:73a831f8108f12a5</T>
      <T n="text">0xC91A0430<!--String: "If you start drawing on an existing wall, you'll get a wall railing. Wall railings function exactly as walls.\n\nProTip: You can also create wall railings by choosing Build Fence from a Wall context menu. And then apply a new fence style via the Replace Fence tool."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="triggers">
